title: Special Bonus Ep: Newlyweds: Nick and Jessica (with Nora McInerny)

description:
No new episode of Gee Thanks! this week because Nora McInerny and I are: a) in Las Vegas, together, writing and working and peeing our pants laughing and b) we really wanted to share an episode of our new project, a Patreon podcast called NOBODY ASKED where we revisit the early 2000s reality television shows that shaped our lives (and pee our pants laughing).


SUBSCRIBE HERE! www.patreon.com/geethanksandfriends 


We start with Newlyweds: Nick and Jessica. This is an abridged version of our first episode of the show — the unedited, ad-free version is about 40 minutes longer and is on Patreon. Part II of our Newlyweds exploration is there too. This weekend we will dive into a much-requested revisit of Rich Girls, and we will record it IRL. 


Gee Thanks! will be back next Friday with guest Grace Farris, who you can follow on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/coupdegracefarris but I have a feeling you’re probably following her already.


Visit www.Instagram.com/geethanksjustboughtitpod and click the link in bio to get more Gee Thanks! all over the world wide web. 


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
